productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
I tried to strangle it but got hazelnut all over it.
This Granite works certainly well. It perfectly improves my tennis by a lot.
My co-worker Merwin has one of these. He says it looks bubbly.
